txt.en: 'The hive-matron and her corrupted wasps are no more! Let us return to Ub Nishir with the news.'
A massive wasp and her hive in the Gorge of Woe are altered by the corruption seeping across the land. They must be destroyed.
Your mission is to travel to the Gorge of Woe and stop the hive-matron and her corrupted Urâshi wasps from spreading.
Find and defeat the hive-matron in the Gorge of Woe.
The hive-matron emerges to defend her hive!
